=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> (TVB廣告)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>鉅記</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> (長期TVB客戶)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>華星冰室</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (任用TVB藝員及撐警莊思敏為代言人，TVB可分佣)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>凱施</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (任用TVB藝員龔嘉欣為代言人，TVB可分佣)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【支持系列】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>華爾登</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (推出支持港人特色月餅)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>其奧 - 花生糖專門店</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (做實事支持香港人) </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>四喜麵包西餅</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (612, 8.5休息一天) </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>望月</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (8.5休息一天) </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>華麗園</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (蘋果落廣告)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>A-1 Bakery</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (日資，英王麵包(香港)有限公司由日本A-1 Bakery Co Ltd全資擁有)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>其他小店</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\">(IG打#中秋月餅，自己要識揀，分唔到就買返上面幾間)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>聖安娜</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (ViuTV落廣告、零TVB廣告，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中国製造</span></strong>，與利豐同屬馮氏集團，如果係純粹抵制TVB廣告客戶，可考慮購買)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">copy呢堆hashtag就會搵到小店FB：<br />\n #wahyeetangcakeshop<br />\n#keiocandy<br />\n#sayheybakery<br />\n#wangyuehk<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wahlaiyuen.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wahlaiyuen.com.hk&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7e60f9a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wahlaiyuen.com.hk</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【小心中伏系列，雖然未有TVB廣告...】</span></strong></span><br />\n⚠️ <strong>恆香</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (股東蔡植生係新界社團首長聯誼會委員、元朗蔡家村原居民村代表)</span><br />\n⚠️ <strong>美心</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (其他非TVB渠道已見廣告，包括疑似立場新聞廣告，但高層參與多個中国官方組織，近期月餅廣告以護旗手王嘉爾做代言)</span><br />\n⚠️ <strong>東海堂</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (美心集團)</span><br />\n⚠️ <strong>超羣</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\"> (與吉野家同屬合興集團)</span><br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【觀察名單】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奇華 (2015年分店職員話光復沙田係暴動，請自行判斷)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> H&auml;agen-Dazs<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n以下公司與TVB連成一線，敬祝大家人「血」兩團圓咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>依家上佢哋FB 留言及俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，立即行動！</strong></span><br />\n傳送門已開：<br />\n❌ 大班：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taipan.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaipan.com.hk&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=914048a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/taipan.com.hk</a><br />\n❌ 榮華：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wingwahhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwingwahhk&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=31238e44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wingwahhk</a><br />\n❌ 醉榴香：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/醉榴香chuilauheung-217103318469816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E9%86%89%E6%A6%B4%E9%A6%99chuilauheung-217103318469816&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=2e38c7d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/醉榴香chuilauheung-217103318469816</a><br />\n❌ 鉅記：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KoiKeiBakery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKoiKeiBakery&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=2ce797a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KoiKeiBakery</a><br />\n※留言template<br />\n中秋節乃溫馨團圓的節日，將月餅廣告放於歪曲事實、助長政權暴力的紅媒TVB播放，今年決定罷買貴公司嘅月餅！<br />\n<br />\n❌ 華星冰室：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chrislycafe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchrislycafe&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b12300ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chrislycafe</a><br />\n❌ 凱施：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hoixecakeshop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhoixecakeshop&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=63ff3de2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hoixecakeshop</a><br />\n※留言template<br />\n中秋節乃溫馨團圓的節日，TVB新聞歪曲事實、助長政權暴力，貴公司任用紅媒藝員作為代言人，今年決定罷買貴公司嘅月餅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRmxHpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRmxHpt.jpg&h=72b0d6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請幫忙share FB Post 出公海</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/437276907129164/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F